prodNameC: 諾法鐵抗德國麻疹病毒免疫球蛋白G酵素免疫分析套組
ingredientsDesc:
Rubella Virus Coated Wells (IgG): coated with Rubella Virus antigen.
IgG Sample Diluent: containing 100 ml of buffer for sample dilution.
Stop Solution: containing 15 ml sulphuric acid, 0.2 mol/l
Washing Solution (20x conc.): containing 50 ml of a 20-fold concentrated buffer for washing the wells.
Rubella Virus anti-IgG Conjugate: containing 20 ml of peroxidase labelled antibodies to human IgG
TMB Substrate Solution: containing 15 ml 3,3’,5,5’-tetramethylbenzidine (TMB) 
Rubella. Virus IgG Standards:
Standard A: 0 IU/ml;
Standard B: 10 IU/ml;
Standard C: 50 IU/ml;
Standard D: 100 IU/ml
